{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"3dc89804fe","title":"给楚荣臻“的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"95767d3544","index":0,"year":1939,"month":3,"day":18,"articleId":"3dc89804fe"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji13","name":"毛泽东全集第13卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji13.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji13":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"e3b5c74577","type":"paragraph","text":"给楚荣臻“的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"3dc89804fe"},{"id":"2126c9b626","type":"paragraph","text":"（1939年3月18日）荣臻同志：你著的书”及送我的一本照片，还有你的信，均收到。这些都是十分宝贵的东西。书准备在延安重庆两处出版（我与王主任P各作一序），照片正传观各同志。望努力奋斗，加深研究，写出更多的新作品。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"3dc89804fe"},{"id":"dd37c517a0","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东[1]最荣臻（1899-1992），四川江海人。当时任中共中央晋察分局书记、智察算军区司令员兼政治委员。[2]指爱荣珠写的介绍晋察囊根据地抗日斗争情况的一本书。毛泽东题写的书名是抗日模范视据地晋察翼边区》.1939年12月由延安八路军军政杂志社出版。毛泽东、来德、王夜样分别为这本书写了序言。[3]指王祥。当时任中央军委副主席兼总政治部主任。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"3dc89804fe"}],"page":{"id":"6616c65ddd","publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"3dc89804fe","start":267,"end":267}}}},"__N_SSG":true}